<div class="project-text">
    <h3>The Project</h3>
    <p>What can be difficult in a UI project that is mostly already built and comes with near-complete guidelines? The icons. Every Stellantis online car dealer had inconsistent iconography, which left users slightly disoriented when comparing vehicle specs from one site to another.</p>
    <p>Standardizing them required getting agencies, companies and suppliers to agree on a single direction, which is rarely a simple conversation. In the end everyone came out satisfied, with a new standard icon set covering every possible specification of a vehicle sold by the group.</p>
